{"tid":1133953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱發現咗個喺人多嘅地方唔駛同人迫嘅方法","createTime":"2019-05-01T12:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:37:25.000Z","uid":150100,"like":11,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6de69f5a27ebd59c4fdd563ecee3175326628ee1","tid":1133953,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n唔知係咪因咩五一黃金週<br />\n周圍都好撚多人<br />\n咁啱今日我又趕時間<br />\n搞到我越迫越燥<br />\n最後我終於忍唔撚住<br />\n一嘢大嗌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邪&middot;王&middot;炎&middot;殺&middot;黑&middot;龍&middot;波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後前面啲人群即刻散開晒，帶住恐懼嘅眼神望住我，仿佛喺度求我唔好出招燒到佢地變成灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我就舒舒服服咁喺佢地中間行過<br />\n終於唔使同人迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依招邪王炎殺黑龍波真係駕世，唔駛真係用出嚟，淨係個名都嚇到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a6d0142f874926e09839325448c891a634e73","tid":1133953,"uid":12707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"樓主又癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad8838bd762059613f8150dcec100fb727f8fa0","tid":1133953,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫佢地跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632aedf4c3b5aa005ca05d6f8e61dea4a9b6e6e5","tid":1133953,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"樓主太型了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想幫你含ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":